---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import Base from '../../../layouts/Base.astro';
import ArticleStats from '../../../components/ArticleStats.astro';

import fuegoDeCana from '../../../assets/writings/fuego-de-cana/01-fuego-de-cana.jpg';
---

<Base title="Fuego de Caña — Vivian Cromwell" activeNav="writings">
  <div class="painting-back">
    <a href="/writings" class="back-link">&larr; Back to Writings</a>
  </div>

  <article class="article" data-pagefind-body>
    <header class="article-header">
      <h1 class="article-title">Fuego de Caña</h1>
      <div class="article-meta">
        <time datetime="2019-06-03">June 3, 2019</time>
        <span class="article-meta-sep">&middot;</span>
        <span class="article-reading-time">2 min read</span>
        <span class="article-meta-sep">&middot;</span>
        <a href="/writings?category=wine-spirits" class="article-category">Wine & Spirits</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="article-body">
      <figure class="article-image">
        <Image src={fuegoDeCana} alt="Fuego de Caña cocktail with burnt marshmallow garnish" widths={[600, 900, 1200]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 700px" loading="eager" />
      </figure>

      <p>Flor de Caña is a Fair Trade certified rum who takes pride in labor conditions and economic opportunity for workers. It is also distilled with 100% renewable energy.</p>

      <p>Today, I am celebrating the global Fair Trade movement with Flor de Caña with this little Mai Tai riff by pairing it with banana and peanut flavor. The little marshmallow is on fire because Flor de Caña, a rum distillery is at the base of an active volcano in Nicaragua.</p>

      <h2>Recipe</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>2 oz peanut washed Flor de Caña 12 years</li>
        <li>0.25 oz Banana liqueur</li>
        <li>0.75 oz lime juice</li>
        <li>0.5 oz orgeat</li>
        <li>0.5 Strega liqueur</li>
        <li>Garnish: ming sprigs, lime, and burnt marshmallow</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Both ming and lime are sourced from our local Farmer's Market, a nod to Fuego de Caña's practice on Fair Trade.</p>

      <p>What is your volcanico?</p>
    </div>

    <ArticleStats slug="fuego-de-cana" tags={["rum", "cocktails"]} />
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .article {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .article-header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0 var(--space-lg);
  }

  .article-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(var(--text-2xl), 5vw, var(--text-3xl));
    font-weight: 400;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .article-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .article-meta-sep {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .article-reading-time {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
  }

  .article-category {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    font-size: var(--text-label);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .article-category:hover {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .article-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: var(--leading-loose);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .article-body h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: var(--space-xl) 0 var(--space-md);
  }

  .article-body h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: var(--space-xl) 0 var(--space-md);
  }

  .article-body p {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-md);
  }

  .article-body a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .article-body a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent-hover);
  }

  .article-image {
    margin: var(--space-lg) 0;
  }

  .article-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .article-image figcaption {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-top: var(--space-xs);
    text-align: center;
    font-style: italic;
  }






</style>
